"1  3 1/2- to 4-pound chicken,  cut into 8 pieces","1  yellow onion, cut into 1-inch wedges","2  small sweet potatoes, peeled and cut into 1-inch chunks","2 tablespoons olive oil","1 teaspoon kosher salt","1/4 teaspoon black pepper","3 tablespoons maple syrup","6  sprigs fresh thyme"